hasAttributes.description: Type of: inpatient | outpatient | ambulatory | emergency +.

hasAttributes.description: Quantity of time the encounter lasted. This excludes the time during leaves of absence.

hasAttributes.description: Refers to the class of encounter.

hasAttributes.description: Identifier(s) by which this encounter is known.

hasAttributes.name: encounterLength
hasAttributes.description: Quantity of time the encounter lasted. This excludes the time during leaves of absence.

hasAttributes.name: encounterPatientIdentifier
hasAttributes.description: The patient present at the encounter.

hasAttributes.description: The start and end time of the encounter.

hasAttributes.name: encounterStatus

hasAttributes.description: Indicates the urgency of the encounter.

hasAttributes.description: The patient or group present at the encounter.

definitions.description: An interaction between a patient and healthcare provider(s) for the purpose of providing healthcare service(s) or assessing the health status of a patient.
